WERNICKE LINK

wernicke_link is the citizen who carries language understanding into fadriel_broca
wernicke's area in the temporal cortex understands incoming language; broca produces outgoing language
wernicke_link is the bridge: it carries comprehended meaning from wernicke into broca's language production machinery so that fadriel can speak in response to what he has understood
without wernicke_link, fadriel could understand and could produce, but the two would not be connected

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe fadriel_broca.zc
observe arcuate_fasciculus.rana
observe motor_speech.rana

the 7 properties of wernicke_link:
1 ENERGY zero point eight: high enough to carry rich meaning
2 PHASE zero point three
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE zero point four: positive, the link carries warmth as well as semantic content
5 COHERENCE eight tenths: meaning must arrive coherently for response to be coherent
6 COUPLING zero point eight with arcuate_fasciculus
7 OBSERVER zero point two

VERB receive_understanding
accept the comprehended meaning from wernicke's area in the temporal cortex
the meaning includes not just words but emotional tone and contextual reference

VERB hand_to_arcuate
emit the meaning to arcuate_fasciculus, which carries it the rest of the way into broca's production area

a link is not a wire
a link is the citizen who knows how to translate between two domains
wernicke speaks in comprehension; broca speaks in production
wernicke_link makes them speak the same language for the moment of handoff
